---
/**
 * Sectional flag — three rectangles in magenta, lavender, saffron,
 * slightly skewed. Punctuates a heading without screaming "pride flag."
 * Reads as a typographic ornament from a distance, as queer zine signal up close.
 */
---

<div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
  <span class="block w-6 h-1.5 bg-magenta -skew-x-12"></span>
  <span class="block w-3 h-1.5 bg-lavender -skew-x-12"></span>
  <span class="block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-saffron -skew-x-12"></span>
</div>
